regulate the heat to a specific predetermined value. The 
thermostatic switch disconnects the supply when the 
predetermined value is reachedandreconnects the supply 
when the iron cools down.   Aturning knob with a   dial just 
below the handle, markedas rayon, cotton, silk, wool etc. 
can be operated to select the   preset temperature. 
