 Objectives: At the end of this lesson you shall be able to 
¢ explain the food mixer and its features 
¢ state the maintenance and service procedures of mixer 
¢   list their common problems, causes and suggest remedial measures. 
 Food   mixer 
 It is an electric domestic appliance which is used to mix, 
juice, grind and blend the fruits and food grains. 
Amediumsized universal motor is used init. Fig 1 shows 
anexploded view of a mixer. 
