be tested)   intest tube,   8 ml oil 1 ml of rectified spirit is 
added and mixture isto be gently shakened. Further 1 ml 
of solution of 0.0085 N sodium carbonate added.   After 
shaking the test tube once again 5 drops of universal 
indicator is added.   The resulting mixture develops a 
colour depending on the acidity value of the mixture. 
